BT 1 0 0 1 0 99 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (The Wike Coherence framework describes the ordered phase \(gamma < gamma_c\) thoroughly but leaves the disordered) Tj T* (phase \(gamma > gamma_c\) largely uncharacterized -- simply "C is low." This paper fills that gap. Treatment-resistant) Tj T* (mental illness is an Edwards-Anderson spin glass: frustrated neural couplings J_ij of mixed sign create an exponentially) Tj T* -0.051 Tw (complex landscape of metastable states. The Edwards-Anderson order parameter q_EA \(mood autocorrelation plateau\) is a) Tj T* 0 Tw (measurable predictor of treatment resistance. Standard antidepressants \(uniform field\) fail for spin glasses because they) Tj T* (shift all valleys equally without restructuring the landscape. Ketamine works by thermal quench through T_g \(melting the) Tj T* (glass\). Psychedelics work by slow annealing above T_g. EMDR works for PTSD \(few deep valleys from fast Kibble-Zurek) Tj T* (quench\) but not depression \(many shallow valleys from slow quench\). Parisi replica symmetry breaking explains why every) Tj T* (patient's illness is structurally unique.) Tj T* ET
